With OTTfeed you can lease a custom Roku SDK channel, instead of paying thousands of dollars upfront and waiting months for development. With this option, the cost will be a fraction of the price and your custom Roku SDK channel will be ready in 5 business days.

No more waiting 24 hours for Roku Direct Publisher to ingest your content and update your channel. With our OTTfeed platform, your custom Roku SDK channel's content will be updated instantly.

Our custom Roku SDK channel supports all types of video content; livestream, series, episodic, short-form, movies and TV specials.

With our custom channels you will get access to our technical support and OTT best practices. We will help you publish your channel to the Roku store.